<sect2>
<title>Installation de <application>GStreamer</application></title>

<para>Installez <application>GStreamer</application> en lançant les commandes
suivantes:</para>

<screen><userinput><command>./configure --prefix=$GNOME_PREFIX --localstatedir=/var/lib  &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install &amp;&amp;
gst-register</command> </userinput></screen>

</sect2>

